      "comment": "SARSAPARILLA KID (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (23.08) last time in a Free For All at Geelong. Has a good record at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Can make amends. DESPICABLE ANDY (3) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (25.18) in a Grade 5 at Sale latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can hit the frame this time. SOMERTON ANN (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.3 lengths from the winner Mick Swagger in third(20.31) at this track. Will give a great sight again. PAW INGRID (6) looks an each-way chance.",
